Package owlSpeak.plugin

This package provides all classes of the plugin modules.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExtRecog
    Class ExtRecog: Plugin to use a external Speechrecognizer
    ExtSynset
    The class that represents the extended Synsets.
    FileCopy
    Class FileCopy: Handles the copy of the wav-file for logging
    GerNet
    Class GerNet: Plugin to handle a NOMATCH using GermaNet
    Keyword
    The class that represents the keywords from the ontology and the recognized result.
    KeywordLists
    Class KeywordLists: Plugin to generate Keyword-Lists from actual context
    Levenshtein
    Class Levenshtein: Plugin to handle a NOMATCH using Levenshtein
    Result
    The class that represents the results from the plugins.
    SameFileRenamePolicy  
    Spotting
    Class Keywordspotting: Plugin to handle a NOMATCH using Keywordspotting with Freetext-Grammar
